WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:16.920
music

00:46.920 --> 01:06.280
It's a quarter to four and I have a production meeting app for it.

01:06.280 --> 01:10.840
I plan to take you for a ride in Central Park in a horse and carriage.

01:10.840 --> 01:13.440
Harry I'd love to but I have work to do.

01:14.160 --> 01:16.240
Okay we'll walk back to your office with you.

01:17.840 --> 01:19.200
So nice out.

01:20.000 --> 01:24.800
I decided to forget about my accounting problems and just enjoy this beautiful spring day.

01:26.160 --> 01:27.120
Take the time Susan.

01:28.080 --> 01:32.480
I know I should but well there are too many things to do.

01:34.000 --> 01:36.640
I understand I'll go for the ride with Michelle.

01:37.600 --> 01:42.880
Right well I had a really nice time.

01:43.440 --> 01:45.440
So did I.

01:45.440 --> 01:47.440
I'm sorry you can't come with us, Susan.

01:48.400 --> 01:50.400
So am I.

01:50.400 --> 01:52.400
Bye bye.

01:53.360 --> 01:55.360
Harry Michelle.

01:57.600 --> 02:00.080
Can you wait till I make a phone call?

02:01.520 --> 02:03.520
Sure.

02:14.400 --> 02:17.440
Susan Stewart's office.

02:18.480 --> 02:19.840
Sam this is Susan.

02:19.840 --> 02:21.280
Hi how was lunch?

02:21.280 --> 02:21.600
Fine.

02:22.880 --> 02:23.360
You're late.

02:24.320 --> 02:27.120
The production department's waiting in the conference room.

02:27.120 --> 02:27.920
I know.

02:27.920 --> 02:31.600
As Paul Smith to fill in for me he knows everything about the production schedule

02:31.600 --> 02:33.280
and he can answer any questions.

02:33.280 --> 02:33.600
Right.

02:34.480 --> 02:37.840
Don't tell anyone but I'm taking a little time to smell the flowers.

02:38.800 --> 02:40.480
Good for you it'll be our secret.

02:40.480 --> 02:42.800
But schedule another production meeting for tomorrow.

02:42.800 --> 02:45.440
I'll be back for my six o'clock appointment with Mr. Rosawa.

02:45.440 --> 02:47.200
Okay Susan and have a nice afternoon.

02:47.200 --> 02:48.160
Thanks.

03:10.480 --> 03:33.200
I know I like her.

03:33.200 --> 03:34.160
How'd you do?

03:34.160 --> 03:35.200
We had a talk.

03:35.920 --> 03:36.400
About what?

03:37.200 --> 03:37.600
Lights.

03:38.800 --> 03:39.600
And what'd you decide?

03:40.480 --> 03:41.280
That's a secret.

03:42.160 --> 03:43.040
Can you get a swimming?

